  "prompt": "Who is the best doctor for cardiology in India?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" cardiologist in India can be subjective, as it often depends on individual patient needs, specific conditions, and personal preferences. However, several renowned cardiologists in India are widely recognized for their expertise and contributions to the field. Some of these include:\n\n1. **Dr. Devi Shetty** - Founder of Narayana Health, he is known for his work in cardiac surgery and has been influential in making cardiac care more affordable.\n\n2. **Dr. TM Ananthakrishnan** - Known for his expertise in interventional cardiology and has had a significant impact on the healthcare system in India.\n\n3. **Dr. Ashok Seth** - A well-known interventional cardiologist, he has performed numerous complex cardiac procedures and is the chairman of Fortis Escorts Heart Institute in New Delhi.\n\n4. **Dr. K. K. Talwar** - Former Director of the Postgraduate Institute of Medical Education and Research (PGIMER) in Chandigarh, he is recognized for his research and clinical contributions.\n\n5. **Dr. Naresh Trehan** - A prominent cardiac surgeon and founder of Medanta - The Medicity, he has performed thousands of heart surgeries.\n\nWhen looking for a cardiologist, it's important to consider factors such as their qualifications, experience, specialties, and patient reviews. It\u2019s advisable to consult with your primary healthcare provider for recommendations that suit your specific health needs.",
